/API/XRWebGLBinding\"><code>XRWebGLBinding</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRWebGLDepthInformation\"><code>XRWebGLDepthInformation</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRWebGLLayer\"><code>XRWebGLLayer</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>This is an <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Writing_guidelines/Experimental_deprecated_obsolete#experimental\">experimental technology</a></strong><br>Check the <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">Browser compatibility table</a> carefully before using this in production.</p></div>\n<p>The <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRView\"><code>XRView</code></a> interface's read-only <strong><code>isFirstPersonObserver</code></strong> property is a boolean indicating if the <code>XRView</code> is a first-person observer view.</p>\n<p>To create video recordings of AR device cameras, you can't simply use one of the rendered eyes, as there often will be a physical offset. Some devices expose a secondary view, the first-person observer view, which has an <code>eye</code> of <code>none</code>.</p>\n<p>To receive a first-person observer view, you need to enable the \"secondary-views\" feature descriptor explicitly (typically as an optional feature). See <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRSystem/requestSession\"><code>XRSystem.requestSession()</code></a> for details.</p>\n<p>The <code>isFirstPersonObserver</code> property then allows you to check which secondary view is a first-person observer view.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"checking_for_first-person_observer_views","title":"Checking for first-person observer views","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// Make sure to enable \"secondary-view\"</span>\nnavigator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>xr<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">requestSession</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"immersive-ar\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">optionalFeatures</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"secondary-views\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">session</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// â€¦</span>\n\n  session<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">requestAnimationFrame</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">frame</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> views <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> frame<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getViewerPose</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>space<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// Make sure to iterate over all views</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> view <span class=\"token keyword\">of</span> views<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>view<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>isFirstPersonObserver<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token function\">renderFPO</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://immersive-web.github.io/webxr-ar-module/#dom-xrview-isfirstpersonobserver","title":"WebXR Augmented Reality Module - Level 1"}],"query":"api.XRView.isFirstPersonObserver"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.XRView.isFirstPersonObserver","dataURL":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRView/isFirstPersonObserver/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Examples","id":"examples"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"The XRView interface's read-only isFirstPersonObserver property is a boolean indicating if the XRView is a first-person observer view.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-09-09T05:23:40.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/xrview/isfirstpersonobserver","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/api/xrview/isfirstpersonobserver/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/073f70e052ff92ab715df3c20678c11c9b51747f","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRView","title":"XRView"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRView/isFirstPersonObserver","title":"XRView.isFirstPersonObserver"}],"pageTitle":"XRView.isFirstPersonObserver - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false}}